-- N4b front-end cross-check artifact: a scalar Evident claim that BOTH the
-- legacy runtime and runtime-smt's front-end can consume.
--
--   legacy:      evident sample runtime-smt/crosscheck/scalar.ev sat_band   => sat
--   runtime-smt: runtime-smt transpile runtime-smt/crosscheck/scalar.ev     => sat
--
-- The front-end (frontend.rs) parses this claim, emits SMT-LIB, and solves it
-- via the same Z3 floor — the verdict must match the oracle's.
claim sat_band
    n ∈ Nat
    n > 5
    n < 8
